传送门：<a href="https://www.zhangxinxu.com/wordpress/2009/08/css-margin%e7%9a%84%e7%9b%b8%e5%85%b3%e5%b1%9e%e6%80%a7%ef%bc%8c%e9%97%ae%e9%a2%98%e5%8f%8a%e5%ba%94%e7%94%a8/#two2">css margin的相关属性，问题及应用</a></p>

<h4 id="情况描述">情况描述</h4>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200324165120419.png#pic_center" alt="选区图例" />
<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200324165318994.png#pic_center" alt="选区图例" />
？这俩的·margin·怎么都保留了  陷入沉思</p>

<h4 id="原因分析">原因分析</h4>
<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">footer</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="nl">display</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">flex</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="nl">justify-content</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">center</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="nl">align-items</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="nb">center</span><span class="p">;</span>
    <span class="nl">flex-direction</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="n">column</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>

</code></pre></div></div>
<p>查看代码之后，发现因为设置了弹性布局
<code class="highlighter-rouge">footer</code>容器被设置为弹性盒子，并且设置子项的文档流方向是纵向的，所以导致出现了截图中的情况
<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200324174006432.PNG?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3FxXzQ0NTM3NDE0,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center" alt="变化过程图例" />
可以作为阻止<code class="highlighter-rouge">margin</code>重叠的一种解决办法 :-）</p>
